  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">On January 1, 2015, a city&rsquo;s minimum hourly wage was $9.25. It will increase by $0.50 on the first day of the year for the next 5 years. Which of the following functions best models the minimum hourly wage, in dollars, <span class=\"italic\">x</span> years after January 1, 2015, where <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"x equals the following five values: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5\"></span></span> ?</p>\n",
